	<body>
		<p>The fireplace turns out to be just as cramped as it appeared, although it will soon be much cleaner as your hands, knees and clothes are scrubbing off the worst of the soot. Unexpectedly, there are no switches, hidden panels, secret compartments or mysterious engravings.</p><p><a href="7965bc7f18b10cf0037084d11612bb0cf5ebf5b6.xhtml">Look around the Library</a>.</p>
